<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>sẖạyl ṣlyby̱</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 sẖạyl ṣlyby wrạk ạ̉nạ wmạsẖy
 ʿạlm rkẖyṣ dnyạ mạtswạsẖy
 wạ̹nt ạlly gẖạly yạ yswʿ wḥdk
 wạ̉y ḥạjẗ ʿlyk mạtgẖlạsẖy
 ạ̉nạ mrkby ḍd ạlgẖrq ʿlsẖạn yswʿ fyhạ
 ạ̉mwạj ʿwạṣf kl dạ byʿml ḥsạb lyhạ
 yạ yswʿ ʿly̱ br ạlnjạẗ ạmty̱ twdyhạ? ạ̹mty̱
 hạfḍl mʿạk wlạ ạ̉y sẖyʾ ạ̉bdaⁿạ hymnʿny
 mạnạ lw kẖsrt ḥyạty ạ̹yh fy ạlkwn hynfʿny
 ạ̉nạ tbʿtk wqt lmạ qlt ly ạtbʿny ạ̹nt
 wmhmạ ạ̉qạbl mn mkẖạṭr ạ̉w msẖạkl ạ̉w ạ̉dẖy̱
 ạ̉nạ brḍw qạbl kl dạ ʿlsẖạn ḥyạẗ ạltlmdẖẗ
 wqt ạlmkẖạwf msẖ bạkẖạf wqt ạlhmwm ạ̉nạ qlby
 sẖạf
 sydy ạlmsyḥ jạyb frḥ jạyb slạm bạʿt ʿzạ
 lạqyt ḥbyby ạ̹zạy yạ nạsy mn ạ̹ydy tạny ạ̉ḍyʿh
 ṣwth ạljmyl ly dlyl dạymaⁿạ bạṭyʿh wạ̉smʿh</lyrics>
<author>rmzy bsẖạrẗ, sạmḥ ʿbyd</author>
